# Legacy in-repo session dir: older builds resolved the default config's
# relative `.qmux/workspaces` into the checkout. State now lives in ~/.qmux, but
# keep this ignored so a pre-existing .qmux/ (state.json, the control socket,
# per-pane scrollback) is never accidentally committed.
.qmux/